# --- Helm ---
Chart.lock
**/charts/*.tgz
# Exception: Flux's source-controller (GitRepository-sourced charts) only resolves the
# *top-level* chart's own immediate dependencies from what's on disk — it does not run a
# recursive `helm dependency build` into subcharts, so a wrapper chart's own *nested* vendored
# dependency (keycloak/minio — see infra/helm/beekeepingit/README.md) must be committed, or Flux
# silently renders the wrapper's own templates but none of the vendored chart's (verified: a
# fresh checkout without these committed produces zero Deployment/StatefulSet/Service for
# keycloak/minio). Every other `charts/*.tgz` (the umbrella's own local file:// deps, and these
# two wrappers' own Chart.lock) stays ignored/regenerated.
!infra/helm/beekeepingit/charts/keycloak/charts/*.tgz
!infra/helm/beekeepingit/charts/minio/charts/*.tgz

# --- Dev tooling (mise / go-task / lefthook) ---
.task/                 # go-task cache
mise.local.toml        # personal mise overrides (not committed)
.mise.local.toml
lefthook-local.yml     # personal lefthook overrides

